`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`So for this step, the only task you need to do is to aggregate all the icons inside a map which then can be used in the `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`Icon.js`}</inlineCode>{` component. This is the corresponding snippet:`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-javascript"
      }}>{`const iconMapContent = [
