`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`The last thing to do is to create the `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`Icon`}</inlineCode>{` component for Web. The idea behind this component is to maintain the props between Web and Native. This will make the use of the component platform agnostic, saving a lot of time when developing.`}</p>
