    <ul>
      <li parentName="ul"><inlineCode parentName="li">{`name`}</inlineCode>{`: the name of the file of the icon. This prop is specified by the `}<inlineCode parentName="li">{`Icon/index.js`}</inlineCode>{` when you import a specific icon`}</li>
